## ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENTS FOR USE

By using this code, you agree to:

✅ **Star the repository** — Show your support on GitHub
   → https://github.com/kustbots/kustmusic

✅ **Fork the repository** — Create your own copy for deployment
   → Never deploy directly from the original repo (Render/Koyeb ban)

✅ **Give credit** — In your bot's /start message or about section:
   → Mention "Powered by Kust Music Bot" or link back to the original repo
   → Credit helps the project grow and is a simple way to show appreciation

✅ **Keep the license** — Include this LICENSE file in any public forks
   → Maintain attribution to the original creators

