## WHAT YOU CAN DO

✅ Use the code for personal projects
✅ Modify and customize the code
✅ Deploy on Render, Koyeb, Railway, Heroku, VPS, or cloud platforms
✅ Create your own version and improve it
✅ Share improvements via pull requests
✅ Use in open-source projects (with proper credit)

## WHAT YOU CANNOT DO

❌ Remove or hide the original credits/attribution
❌ Claim the code as entirely your own creation
❌ Use without forking (direct deploy bans the original repo on platforms)
❌ Close-source derivative projects without proper GPL compliance
❌ Remove this license from public distributions

